sampleID: # qc_pass_50pc  - Did 50% of the total reads pass IRMA QC? If below 50%, sample is labelled with FAILED for this column. [total_reads_pass_qc > 50%]
# nomatch_high -  The number of reads not matching the specified organism (FLU or RSV) is greater than matched, FAILED is returned. [nomatch > match]
# match_adequate - The number of matched reads above a minimum threshold (approx. ~50x depth). [reads_match >= min_read]
# alt_metric - Reads matched large number of alternative reference - helps to identify mixture (10% of reads and approx. 25x depth). [altmatch/match > 0.10 & altmatch > min_read_alt]
